{"tid":270060,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"癲狗系列- 港式黑椒汁","createTime":"2017-06-04T05:41:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-10T07:24:25.000Z","uid":74981,"like":57,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a08ce0dc41fa519ceed98ce1a8096fc1754d3ade","tid":270060,"uid":74981,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T05:41:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s9.postimg.org/7z810mhxr/Black_pepper_source.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs9.postimg.org%2F7z810mhxr%2FBlack_pepper_source.jpg&h=d4a21072&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>影片如下:</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/tpSAUQGjb2c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FtpSAUQGjb2c&d=FWGQGMRI8%2BR9BXZI3Qvkeb%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=1b9cc3f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/tpSAUQGjb2c</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>材料:</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n1. 大洋蔥4份1個(或細洋蔥半個)<br />\n<br />\n2. 蒜蓉1茶匙<br />\n<br />\n3. 黑胡椒碎2茶匙<br />\n<br />\n4. 水大半碗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>調味:</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n1. 鹽半茶匙 (可加可不加)<br />\n<br />\n2. 糖1茶匙<br />\n<br />\n3. 美極1湯匙<br />\n<br />\n4. GAP汁1茶匙<br />\n<br />\n5. 茄汁1茶匙<br />\n<br />\n6. 指天椒2隻切碎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>做法:</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n1. 開獲中火燒熱油, 落洋蔥炒至變色.<br />\n<br />\n2. 落蒜蓉, 收細少少水炒, 千其唔好俾佢燶, 否則成個汁就會變味.<br />\n<br />\n3. 同時落黑胡椒碎炒<br />\n<br />\n4. 加水大半碗<br />\n<br />\n5. 落齊以上調味<br />\n<br />\n6. 1茶匙生粉加1茶匙水攪勻, 慢慢落獲埋芡, 完成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n各位巴打絲打，順便一題，由於近日會員肥絲大隻哩隻肥狗進入發情期，成日係本癲狗既post入面搞事，試圖想引本癲狗注意。可惜佢只係一個得158cm高，168磅既核突佬，所以佢連俾我撚既資格都冇。各位如果唔想再俾條垃圾肥閪騷擾，可以學本癲狗咁block柒佢，咁就可以令佢自己單機，如下圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s1.postimg.org/96tm09ykv/Shut_Up.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.postimg.org%2F96tm09ykv%2FShut_Up.png&h=fed42d01&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f3c2c0ccfed9b9131d7bfb1313b0a47c9d8a06b3","tid":270060,"uid":21423,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T05:43:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5fecb1fd6fee617f06d1eb25f065a8712c6d99cc","tid":270060,"uid":73160,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T05:44:16.000Z","msg":"Gap汁好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5cfa832b8b9e04cc2dfc243bf5f0378bb3f3228","tid":270060,"uid":21423,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T05:45:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e7165da86a9687dc19f0a90a579fb889ba6e9e8d","tid":270060,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T05:47:58.000Z","msg":"有冇港式果隻營光茄汁同中式洋蔥汁"},{"pid":"46bf09180ab8418def91f0981002c8439a73a4eb","tid":270060,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T05:49:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Gap汁好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86c146894fa66ec98910f78bcde0718d3d1490d9","tid":270060,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T05:50:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"492dc3b91d4114e80a976696685d7a33be4641c7","tid":270060,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T05:50:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇港式果隻營光茄汁同中式洋蔥汁</blockquote><br />\n洋蔥汁ok，但港式茄汁要研究下，茄汁我淨係識整西式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b169ce4604ca63aaee38d3cf9d411e9e3adbe86b","tid":270060,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T05:50:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"097393ae2e024b44f75fdcdb568769b0e0fb5217","tid":270060,"uid":73160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T05:54:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇港式果隻營光茄汁同中式洋蔥汁</blockquote><br />\n洋蔥汁ok，但港式茄汁要研究下，茄汁我淨係識整西式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n西式係咪乾茄定罐頭油茄？"},{"pid":"5c8e728a7fd825a3c3b7565da301e26a3fc2c4b4","tid":270060,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T05:58:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇港式果隻營光茄汁同中式洋蔥汁</blockquote><br />\n洋蔥汁ok，但港式茄汁要研究下，茄汁我淨係識整西式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n西式係咪乾茄定罐頭油茄？</blockquote><br />\n普通罐頭茄就可<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d67717d38fda20634b021191d21c3f9a2dd89c08","tid":270060,"uid":73160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T06:03:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇港式果隻營光茄汁同中式洋蔥汁</blockquote><br />\n洋蔥汁ok，但港式茄汁要研究下，茄汁我淨係識整西式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n西式係咪乾茄定罐頭油茄？</blockquote><br />\n普通罐頭茄就可<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n通常都係買意粉醬, 有mushroom 同 garlic 味嗰d，罐頭未買過, 不過好以話仲有營養過新鮮番茄"},{"pid":"502112e9560bee1403e4f54ecc803c24712d4b8c","tid":270060,"uid":3037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T06:40:56.000Z","msg":"美極唔是咁用的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd811570f3995a268a03adba4b8b14a6d0415372","tid":270060,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T06:48:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇港式果隻營光茄汁同中式洋蔥汁</blockquote><br />\n洋蔥汁ok，但港式茄汁要研究下，茄汁我淨係識整西式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n西式係咪乾茄定罐頭油茄？</blockquote><br />\n普通罐頭茄就可<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n通常都係買意粉醬, 有mushroom 同 garlic 味嗰d，罐頭未買過, 不過好以話仲有營養過新鮮番茄</blockquote><br />\n罐頭番茄係茄味好d，因為係意大利茄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實自製意粉醬成本唔低，買現成好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2d8e612b0fa462335f5cefb2653dccfdf44a9cd","tid":270060,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T06:58:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>美極唔是咁用的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd4467b12fa5abd72084649de9f78c86394ce0bf","tid":270060,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T07:23:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"754bce101479efd930be91e4c4a74767151edfde","tid":270060,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T07:26:28.000Z","msg":"目測: 肥絲有9條契仔路過此地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"994b59664f724a8c938a80d999065fc6bedb7883","tid":270060,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T07:32:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"becd462c867f053e38a84f09e2a6360083d42e5c","tid":270060,"uid":1096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T07:34:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84ca0eee12bea6a03f8b19c37fa6c99d6675a62f","tid":270060,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T07:34:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b719dff0ac1fdba7629e216b088c1fd1d564cbc6