g src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打有留意我之前既片，多謝支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係呀，雞扒併黑椒汁一流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n成日去茶記見到都會叫黑椒雞扒飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又平又開胃</blockquote><br />\n正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"846cd4432f396342a5e19c3378722a5f4d6c084c","tid":270060,"uid":19300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T14:58:58.000Z","msg":"食開啲黑椒汁都有陣不必要嘅辣味<br />\n唔係難食嘅 但唔洗咁重手掛<br />\n唔知樓主嗰隻點<br />\n遲啲試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fc5e4cb408251febf9c3d08a831b4683bd29451","tid":270060,"uid":33731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T15:01:24.000Z","msg":"正啊係外國想食頹飯都難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"933ea85d5934e3f9920f1758401e34bd5c18db4d","tid":270060,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T15:01:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食開啲黑椒汁都有陣不必要嘅辣味<br />\n唔係難食嘅 但唔洗咁重手掛<br />\n唔知樓主嗰隻點<br />\n遲啲試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我哩個係辣既，有加辣椒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果唔想要辣就可以唔加辣椒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec2d7ef8bdf6dfef8aebe2243c2b1550a0852989","tid":270060,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T15:03:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正啊係外國想食頹飯都難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n煎塊豬扒，雞扒，然後加埋我哩個汁，包你滿意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b63f664f91b5b3a24c2c30d37842a23c4e5c9642","tid":270060,"uid":19300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T15:05:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>食開啲黑椒汁都有陣不必要嘅辣味<br />\n唔係難食嘅 但唔洗咁重手掛<br />\n唔知樓主嗰隻點<br />\n遲啲試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我哩個係辣既，有加辣椒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果唔想要辣就可以唔加辣椒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係唔慣茶餐廳嗰隻黑椒辣姐<br />\n辣椒照落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2df93652d9914300c69209236c1d43fa5d0bac30","tid":270060,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T15:07:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>食開啲黑椒汁都有陣不必要嘅辣味<br />\n唔係難食嘅 但唔洗咁重手掛<br />\n唔知樓主嗰隻點<br />\n遲啲試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我哩個係辣既，有加辣椒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果唔想要辣就可以唔加辣椒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係唔慣茶餐廳嗰隻黑椒辣姐<br />\n辣椒照落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n辣椒除左辣，佢仲有一種辣椒香，會令個汁好食好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d71b33a2d78689d182efc744e55fc7871038d58d","tid":270060,"uid":3109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T15:09:25.000Z","msg":"超市嘅蕃茄醬要點整先好食? 就咁加煮完意粉嘅水爆爆佢?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n題外話, 肥絲食唔食豬扒? 如果食, 咁咪即係食同類<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9556dfaade86db14a3c50dc32e07ebcfd3257c61","tid":270060,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T15:25:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>超市嘅蕃茄醬要點整先好食? 就咁加煮完意粉嘅水爆爆佢?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n題外話, 肥絲食唔食豬扒? 如果食, 咁咪即係食同類<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n通常可以先爆爆d洋蔥，再爆下d蒜蓉 (唔好俾佢燶), 再加茄醬同